The '''''Civil Service Yearbook''''' is an annual reference guide to the [[British civil service]] and [[Non-departmental public body|non-departmental public bodies]].

The book is now published by Dandy Booksellers and the fiftieth edition, for 2013-14, was published in March 2014.<ref>[http://www.dandybooksellers.com/acatalog/civil-service-yearbook-50th-edition-2013-2014.html Civil Service Yearbook 50th Edition 2013/14.] Dandy Booksellers. Retrieved 12 December 2014.</ref>

